Install on current machine
    Obsolete:
      cabal install --enable-shared hssqlppp/ hssqlppp-th/
    Current:
      1. (if 2. doesn't work right away)
          source /usr/local/sqream-prerequisites/versions/2.0/bin/use-prerequisites.sh
      2. cabal install --global --package-db=/usr/local/sqream-prerequisites/package-install/ghc-7.6.3-040514 --prefix=/usr/local/sqream-prerequisites/package-install/cabal-7.6.3-040514 --enable-shared hssqlppp/ hssqlppp-th/

Create distribution files

    upgrade version number:
      - in Makefile
      - in .cabal files in folders hssqlppp/ hssqlppp-th/ hssqlppp-pg/
    make sdists
